title: The Frankenstein Monster (Marvel Comics)
description:
Marvels Frankenstein series from the '70s began with a 4-issue retelling of Mary Shelley's original novel, by Gary Friedrich and Mike Ploog. Several more issues continued his story into the 1890s, until he was placed in suspended animation and revived in modern times.

Also included are 'The Monsters' further appearances within the Marvel universe.


Released on http://ComicPirates.info
